gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Bucks 142, Wizards 129
gameRecap.excerpt: The Bucks defeated the Wizards, 142-129. Giannis Antetokounmpo recorded 42 points, 13 rebounds, and eight assists for the Bucks, with Damian Lillard adding 22 points and seven assists in the victory. Jordan Poole tallied a season-high 30 points, along with one rebound and one assist for the Wizards in the losing effort. The Bucks are winners of 5 straight and improve to 10-4 on the season, while the Wizards fall to 2-11.
